Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru always believed in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,More than myself or Neji or\Nany of us here... He is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, fatso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't YOU say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Partial Expansion Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Partial Expansion Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Partial Expansion Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me! Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Expansion Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:55.65,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465,266)}Goodbye, My Friend...!\N I'll Always Believe in You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, My Friend...!\NI'll Always Believe in You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it... Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I had to get to\Nthe second state
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for an opponent like this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slamming Palm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What is that appearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the second state, I can put out ten times\Nmore power than I have thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too painful to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew that the side effects\Nof the Curry Pill would be this intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to a powerless scum for butting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing Ninja better suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hand if you're playing Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper... scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Split!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,99... 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I said, split!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up quietly, the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally caught 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this!\NThe team with Choji always loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a lot of Chakra\Nfor this "second state."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take whatever Chakra\Nyou have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll take them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had nearly enough to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I haven't had enough to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What, just one last piece, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said I haven't had\Nenough to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, you're the scum\Nused as a sacrificial pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Die... you pitiful fatso, the odd man out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you play Ninja with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we let you play,\Nwe'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... then the number\Nof people won't be even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese chess is fun\Nbecause the number of pieces are even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece that is useless is\Nthe same as not having that piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones with fewer people\Nand we're not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's okay with you, then it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we gonna hide this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And um, the whole Akimichi Clan\Nis fat and slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what everyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Choji, you're a kindhearted guy...\Nmore than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you'll surely make friends\Nwho'll see that quality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you should cherish\Nthose friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and be the kind of friends\Nwho believe in each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really make... friends like that...\Nsomeone like me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not the only one\NI'm going to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After I kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the cruel, sleazy,\Nmean guys who used you as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he... promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You better catch up with us... Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's definitely going to defeat\Nthe opponent and come after us...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... he can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! While I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we get Sasuke back\Nbefore Choji catches up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's late... that Jirobo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's greedy and eats so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably squeezing out Chakra\Neven from the marrow of their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he had switched\Nwith me already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I linger,\NI won't be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chili Pepper Pill is left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if I take that...\NI'll die, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare die, Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been doing things together\Nsince that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You... were there just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about playing N inja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a drag,\Nso I pulled myself out from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that's my special seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your special seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to lie on my back and\Nlook at the clouds on a nice day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to look at clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I sit there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good place.\NYou can see the clouds well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,watch the clouds with me\Nand lounge around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know! I-I brought snacks.\NWant some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating potato chips\Nwhile watching clouds... this is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shikamaru...\Nfrom the Nara Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You... What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Choji! Akimichi Choji\Nof the Akimichi Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji, huh...\NI think I'll get along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always do things together\Nfrom now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru... Sorry... I can't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to beat him...\Neven if it means death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do now,\Nit's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Crushing Palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Boulder Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 100 times stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that food\Ncan be a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for people to hold a horrible grudge\Nagainst somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The blow just now...\Nwas for eating the last bite of my snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy has so much Chakra that\Nhis body has changed physically!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for making fun of me by calling me\Na sacrificial pawn and fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I can't forgive you for\Nmore than anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do suffer when\Nyou have a stupid leader. You underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll kill you losers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,before you suffer working\Nunder a glum shadow lover like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should blame your stupid leader\Nfor choosing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You insulted my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,More than mocking me\Nby calling me fat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and poaching the last bite\Nof a four-star meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my Chakra... to my left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, uh-oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This blow... is heavier than my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...! Don't be hasty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a kindhearted guy,\Nmore than everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you'll surely make friends\Nwho'll see that part of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you should cherish\Nthose friends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and be the kind of friends\Nwho believe in each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hurry up and get over here."\NIt's Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everyone's waiting."\NKiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ino-Shika-Cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is just potato chips,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anybody else have\Nthe last piece, no matter who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji and I have worked as a team\Nfor many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so coordinating with him\Nis easiest for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made... a lot of friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin'...
